Package kea.exercise.hogwartsstudentadmin.edu.hogwarts.model

Class Student

java.lang.Object
kea.exercise.hogwartsstudentadmin.edu.hogwarts.model.Student
@Entity public class Student extends Object
The Student class is a model that represents a student in the Hogwarts Student Admin system. It contains information about the name, date of birth, house, prefect status, enrollment year, graduation year, and school year of the student.
